Package com.sri.ai.grinder.interpreter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Assignment
    An interface representing assignments for a set of expressions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractInterpreter
    A Rewriter based on a TopRewriter, adding the functionality of solving quantified and aggregate expressions with a MultiQuantifierEliminator provided by the implementation of an abstract method.
    AbstractIterativeMultiQuantifierEliminator
    An abstract class for quantifier eliminators using a simple (total or sampled) iteration over the domain of the eliminated variables.
    AdderIterator  
    BruteForceAdderIterator
    An adder iterator going over all indices assignments.
    BruteForceCommonInterpreter
    An extension of BruteForceInterpreter using CommonSimplifier.
    BruteForceInterpreter
    An implementation of AbstractInterpreter using BruteForceMultiQuantifierEliminator.
    BruteForceMultiQuantifierEliminator
    An extension of AbstractMultiQuantifierEliminator that solves quantified expressions by brute force.
    ContextAssignmentLookup  
    DefaultAssignment
    An default implementation of Assignment using maps from expressions to expressions.
    SamplingAdderLazyIterator
    A lazy iterator going over a sample of indices assignments.
    SamplingCommonInterpreter
    An extension of SamplingInterpreter using CommonSimplifier.
    SamplingIfNeededMultiQuantifierEliminator
    A quantifier eliminator that decides whether to use brute force or sampling depending on sample size, domain size, and a "always-sample" parameter.
    SamplingInterpreter
    This interpreter will evaluate expressions, but will sample quantifiers instead of using brute force.
    SamplingSingleQuantifierEliminator
    A sampling quantifier elimination for problems with a single index.
    TopRewriterUsingContextAssignments
    A TopRewriter based on another TopRewriter, and adding functionality for replacing expressions by their assignments stored on the context, stored there by AbstractIterativeMultiIndexQuantifierEliminator#extendAssignments(Map newAssignments, Context context).
    TopRewriterUsingContextAssignmentsReceivingBaseTopRewriterAtConstruction
    A convenience variant of TopRewriterUsingContextAssignments that takes its base top rewriter at construction time.
